":30,"bottom_button_padding_vertical":14,"bottom_button_padding_horizontal":32,"bottom_button_bg_color":"#c6a228","bottom_button_text_color":"#ffffff","bottom_button_hover_bg_color":"#be9722","bottom_button_hover_text_color":"#ffffff","bottom_button_font_size":18,"bottom_button_font_weight":600,"bottom_button_border_radius":4,"bottom_button_border_width":0,"bottom_button_border_color":"#c6a228","bottom_button_hover_border_color":"#be9722"},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_cbe10ce_TVhbnb"],"settings":{}},"17805309863eb0c6e6":{"type":"_blocks","blocks":{"ai_gen_block_387c332_GhNaR6":{"type":"ai_gen_block_387c332","settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions About Commercial Laundry Equipment","desktop_width_percent":100,"background_color":"#052b3e","divider_color":"#c6a228","heading_font":"system_ui_n4","heading_color":"#c6a228","question_font":"system_ui_n4","question_color":"#ffffff","question_hover_color":"#c6a228","icon_color":"#c6a228","answer_font":"system_ui_n4","answer_color":"#ffffff","link_color":"#c6a228","link_hover_color":"#be9722","question_1":"Can Bichin Laundry Equipment help me choose the right commercial laundry equipment mix for our laundry operations?","answer_1":"<p>Yes, absolutely! Commercial laundry equipment should be matched to your actual operation — not just your wish list.<\/p><p>The Bichin Laundry Equipment team helps customers think through:<\/p><ul><li>Available square footage<\/li><li>Laundry volume<\/li><li>Peak usage times<\/li><li>Linen or load types<\/li><li>Utility access and installation requirements<\/li><li>Revenue goals<\/li><li>Capacity mix<\/li><li>Workflow efficiency<\/li><li>Future growth<br\/><\/li><\/ul><p>We are here to support you through the entire commercial equipment buying process—layout planning, store design, equipment selection, financing assistance, ordering, installation, programming, demonstration, and ongoing service and maintenance.<\/p>","link_text_1":"We're here to make this experience easier for you, get in touch today!","link_url_1":"shopify:\/\/pages\/contact-us","question_2":"Why do laundry businesses choose to work with Bichin Laundry Equipment? ","answer_2":"<p>Bichin Laundry Equipment is more than a catalog of commercial laundry machines for sale. We work hard to go the extra mile for every customer by providing wide-reaching support in all areas of sales, installations, service, parts, and troubleshooting. Being an <strong>authorized supplier and distributor<\/strong> of Dexter and Huebsch commercial laundry equipment means we are trusted by the manufacturers and our machines are supported by warranties, service, planning help, and ongoing customer care. <\/p><p>We will never “set it and forget it” when you hire us. We are in it for the long haul and we will be here to support you with:<\/p><ul><li>Equipment selection<\/li><li>Laundromat planning<\/li><li>Layout guidance<\/li><li>Installation coordination<\/li><li>Parts access<\/li><li>Maintenance and service<br\/><br\/><\/li><\/ul>","link_text_2":"","link_url_2":"","question_3":"What types of commercial laundry equipment does Bichin Laundry Equipment sell?","answer_3":"<p>Bichin Laundry Equipment supplies Dexter and Huebsch commercial washers, dryers, stack units, on-premise laundry equipment, and other commercial laundry solutions for laundromats and high-volume laundry operations.<\/p>","link_text_3":"","link_url_3":"","question_4":"Does Bichin Laundry Equipment sell equipment for laundromats?","answer_4":"<p>Yes. Laundromats are a major focus, and Bichin Laundry Equipment’s current core customers are laundromat owners. We help with planning, design, equipment selection, installation, and ongoing support for laundromat owners throughout BC, Alberta, and the Yukon.<\/p>","link_text_4":"","link_url_4":"","question_5":"Does Bichin Laundry Equipment also supply equipment for hotels and healthcare facilities?","answer_5":"<p>Yes. Bichin Laundry Equipment currently offers commercial laundry equipment sales for businesses beyond laundromats, including including hotels, healthcare environments, and other businesses with large laundry operations, both vended and On-Premise.<\/p>","link_text_5":"","link_url_5":"","question_6":"Can Bichin Laundry Equipment help me with selecting the right equipment mix?","answer_6":"<p>Yes. Bichin Laundry Equipment’s main mandate is to provide owners and operators of large laundry operations with help designing floor plans, machine mix, quantities, installation, and ongoing support.<\/p>","link_text_6":"","link_url_6":"","question_7":"What brands does Bichin Laundry Equipment carry?","answer_7":"<p>Bichin Laundry Equipment currently offers commercial laundry equipment from <strong>Dexter<\/strong> (both hardmount and softmount models) and Wascomat, as well as small chassis laundry equipment made by Huebsch.<\/p>","link_text_7":"","link_url_7":"","question_8":"Do you offer compact commercial laundry machines for smaller laundry rooms?","answer_8":"<p>Yes. Bichin Laundry Equipment now offers <strong>Huebsch Small Chassis machines<\/strong> for customers who need commercial laundry performance in a smaller footprint. These machines are a strong fit for apartment buildings, hotels, care facilities, staff laundry rooms, and other on-premise laundry spaces where floor space is limited but dependable commercial equipment is still important.<\/p>","link_text_8":"","link_url_8":"","question_9":"","answer_9":"","link_text_9":"","link_url_9":"","question_10":"","answer_10":"","link_text_10":"","link_url_10":""},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["ai_gen_block_387c332_GhNaR6"],"settings":{}}},"order":["main","177672015470975dd7","category_collection_style1_w7zfjE","1776728157fbe80a6c","1776721677e48e5c2e","177672426903bc940e","1776729227a477ad2e","1778536921de8ca656","1780528829f5ff8e75","17805309863eb0c6e6"]}